title: Redis Goes From Open-Source to Fauxpen and the Forks Have Already Started
description:
Redis is only the last in a line of companies who have lately dropped open-source licenses in favor of proprietary open-source lookalike licenses. In this case, a fork has already happened that just might end up being real competition for Redis.

The post Redis Goes From Open-Source to Fauxpen and the Forks Have Already Started appeared first on FOSS Force.
